              <Icon name="mdi:heart" class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600 mb-3" />
              <h3 class="text-xl mb-3">Our Mission</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                To make nutrition approachable, fun, and judgment-free. We believe everyone deserves 
                to enjoy their food without feeling guilty or confused.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-orange-100 rounded-2xl p-6">
              <Icon name="mdi:hand-clap" class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-600 mb-3" />
