              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Serious about health, but not serious about ourselves. We fact-check everything, 
                but we're not afraid to joke about our love for carbs.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-purple-100 rounded-2xl p-6">
              <Icon name="mdi:target" class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600 mb-3" />
              <h3 class="text-xl mb-3">Our Goal</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Help you make food choices that work for YOUR life. No one-size-fits-all diets, 
                no shame, just real talk about real food.
              </p>
            </div>

